[{\"slug\":\"airbrush-makeup-florida-brides\",\"title\":\"Why Airbrush Makeup Is a Game-Changer for Florida Brides\",\"date\":\"2026-03-06T17:42:01.548Z March 6, 2026\",\"category\":\"Bridal\",\"excerpt\":\"Discover why airbrush makeup is the top choice for Florida brides who want a flawless, sweat-proof look all day long.\",\"content\":\"Florida's heat and humidity can be a bride's worst enemy, but airbrush makeup creates a breathable, waterproof barrier that lasts from ceremony to last dance. The ultra-fine mist application delivers buildable coverage that photographs beautifully without looking cakey. For Fort Lauderdale brides, airbrush is the gold standard for staying picture-perfect in any weather.\"}]